messages.content: How do I install the ComfyUI_RErouter_CustomNodes custom nodes?
Navigate to the ComfyUI\custom_nodes directory and clone the repository using the following command: ```git clone https://github.com/an90 vicissray/ComfyUI_RErouter_CustomNodes.git```.
How do I update the ComfyUI_RErouter_CustomNodes custom nodes?

Navigate to the ComfyUI\custom_nodes\ComfyUI_RErouter_CustomNodes directory and pull the latest updates using the following command: ```git pull https://github.com/an90 vicissray/ComfyUI_RErouter_CustomNodes.git```.
